  "body": "# submission name:\r\nvibe_coder_final_boss\r\n\r\n# upload zipped `archive.zip`\r\nhttps://github.com/BradyMeighan/comma_video_compression_challenge/releases/download/vcfb-archive/archive.zip\r\n\r\n# report.txt\r\n```\r\n=== Evaluation config ===\r\n  batch_size: 16\r\n  device: cpu\r\n  num_threads: 2\r\n  prefetch_queue_depth: 4\r\n  report: submissions/vibe_coder_final_boss/report.txt\r\n  seed: 1234\r\n  submission_dir: submissions/vibe_coder_final_boss\r\n  uncompressed_dir: /home/runner/work/comma_video_compression_challenge/comma_video_compression_challenge/videos\r\n  video_names_file: /home/runner/work/comma_video_compression_challenge/comma_video_compression_challenge/public_test_video_names.txt\r\n=== Evaluation results over 600 samples ===\r\n  Average PoseNet Distortion: 0.00049454\r\n  Average SegNet Distortion: 0.00027178\r\n  Submission file size: 197,160 bytes\r\n  Original uncompressed size: 37,545,489 bytes\r\n  Compression Rate: 0.00525123\r\n  Final score: 100*segnet_dist + sqrt(10*posenet_dist) + 25*rate = 0.23\r\n```\r\n\r\n# does your submission require gpu for evaluation (inflation)?\r\nno\r\n\r\n# did you include the compression script? and want it to be merged?\r\nno\r\n\r\n# additional comments\r\nHad a ton of fun. Lots of tokens used in the making of this.\r\n\r\nFull interactive writeup: https://comma-writeup.pages.dev/\r\nSmaller Markdown writeup: https://github.com/BradyMeighan/vibe-coder-final-boss/blob/main/WRITEUP.md\r\nSource: https://github.com/BradyMeighan/vibe-coder-final-boss\r\n\r\nReproduced via the same `eval.yml` workflow on my fork before submitting: https://github.com/BradyMeighan/comma_video_compression_challenge/actions/runs/25306126756 (16m17s on ubuntu-latest, well under the 30-min budget).\r\n",
